Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:04.72,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}放出的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:08.03,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}将梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.03,0:03:11.77,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}悄悄带进了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.81,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:19.01,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}你是否还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:24.19,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}在由心发出呐喊时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:25.65,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}想再看一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:28.68,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}那片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.53,0:03:36.99,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}对自己坦率些最好
