Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:46.61,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}去实现你带给我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.52,0:03:49.13,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur2}请不要悲伤 因为有我守护
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:56.22,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}对自己坦率些最好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:58.96,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur2}不要再一个人去承受风雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:06.23,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}我来为你撑伞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:09.11,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur2}请不要悲伤 因为有我守护
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:59.30,OP3_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}君の瞳は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:04.72,OP3_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}光輝いて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:08.03,OP3_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}僕の瞳に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.03,0:03:11.77,OP3_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}そっと夢を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.81,OP3_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}見せてくれたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:19.01,OP3_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}思い出して欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:24.19,OP3_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}心が叫ぶ時は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:25.65,OP3_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}もう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:28.68,OP3_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}あの空を見たい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.53,0:03:36.99,OP3_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(150,150)\blur2}自分に素直になればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:39.93,OP3_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(150,150)\blur2}君がくれた夢を僕が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:46.61,OP3_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(150,150)\blur2}叶えに旅に出るからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.52,0:03:49.13,OP3_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(150,150)\blur2}悲しまないで僕が守るから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:56.22,OP3_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(150,150)\blur2}自分に素直になればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:58.96,OP3_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(150,150)\blur2}一人で雨に打たれないで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:06.23,OP3_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(150,150)\blur2}僕が傘を差し出すから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:09.11,OP3_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(150,150)\blur2}悲しまないで僕が守るから
